# Root POM Dependency Policy

- Do not add `dependencies` or `dependencyManagement` sections in the root `pom.xml`.
- Root `pom.xml` may contain build/verification plugins and shared plugin configuration only.
- Add runtime/test dependencies in module `pom.xml` files instead.
